{"tid":2157579,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"員工外出倒垃圾 差人稱防盜竊  黃店指警竄入舖 無手令擅翻文件","createTime":"2020-08-15T06:28:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T13:48:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"6516ae3b5c7fd31cf591d03e2a5c087ce9fb656b","tid":2157579,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06:28:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200815/EVIESQOIVVHIDK5YH2IHF2CWCI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200815%2FEVIESQOIVVHIDK5YH2IHF2CWCI%2F&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8aP8PJJZD286lWcuKEclkJo%3D&h=34dd6351\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200815%2FEVIESQOIVVHIDK5YH2IHF2CWCI%2F&h=d89243d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200815/EVIESQOIVVHIDK5YH2IHF2CWCI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n員工外出倒垃圾 差人稱防盜竊 <br />\n黃店指警竄入舖 無手令擅翻文件<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】深水埗大埔道18號黃店「La Tessa」，昨凌晨時分於專頁上張貼多張閉路電視畫面，指上周二（4日）凌晨4時許有五名身穿制服的「公職人員」（警員），趁廚師離開店舖倒垃圾期間，擅自闖入店內翻閱文件，更一度查看店舖收銀機，逗留45分鐘「賴死唔走」。事件惹來店舖負責人不滿，質疑為何警員在沒有任何法庭命令，擅自闖入店內搜查。<br />\n<br />\n警方事後在facebook解釋事件，指當日警員於深水埗大埔道一帶巡邏期間，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Hm67M-_WRywwM4W0qozfdEqQqaE=/1672x1072/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PNN6U3OEVJHBPDJ4TQEO4LBMRI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHm67M-_WRywwM4W0qozfdEqQqaE%3D%2F1672x1072%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPNN6U3OEVJHBPDJ4TQEO4LBMRI.jpg&h=dd4ff6f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■從餐廳閉路電視片段可見，多名警員在收銀櫃枱自行翻閱文件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n包括商業登記及員工資料<br />\n<br />\n就「La Tessa」指控警員不肯離。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n店舖負責人葉先生對本報表明不接受警方解釋，並透露更多事件細節，他指。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n葉先生強調，當日店舖後門不斷有職員出入倒垃圾，而涉事警員來到現場後，便逕自開啟後門入舖。他認為警員正常做法應該是在外等候，而非擅闖店舖，更不是長時間逗留搜查店內物品，形容當時入舖警員是「自己製造罪惡，自己製造搜掠痕迹，而唔係反罪惡」，甚至直言「根本呢啲就係賊」。<br />\n<br />\n他又提到，自己頂手該餐廳約三個月，由於位置十分靠近警察遊樂會，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n身兼大律師的當區區議員劉偉聰認為警方不顧事實基礎，以「防止罪案」為由無視法律對其權力的制約，直言警方解釋是荒謬和無理失據，對此感到遺憾和憤慨，將會全力協助負責人跟進事件。"},{"pid":"2994f65ad14b041ffd2bff4aeed4886dcff323ea","tid":2157579,"uid":276273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06:30:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"568c0872d157a1490323d760521e9d2f652b54ce","tid":2157579,"uid":264245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06:31:31.000Z","msg":"星期一公然無視搜令果陣開始所有警察都已經當正自己國安咁目中無人"},{"pid":"46b1fffcc24a85a9dfba9768f8cbf1c05828032f","tid":2157579,"uid":71561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06:33:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a508db38bc3bd06dba71af0061b5970f26028d18","tid":2157579,"uid":52876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06:36:44.000Z","msg":"賊喊捉賊"},{"pid":"baeb6bee1e18dad8197a345f0f3da2bd927cd9c9","tid":2157579,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06:37:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"61c996ab30b76ab0afa745f142c90bab3e28f6e7","tid":2157579,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06:37:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a366290c576a644831360ef1316586ec733717b","tid":2157579,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T06:39:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gi